name: HUMAN LAST HOPE #1
description:
I made this digital art inspired from my personal thought, that all humans on this earth are equal and similar. We all have the same hope that is "happiness". But in the end of the day, we have to fight alone to reach that hope

if you need my other work please hit me on twitter @Gnaki_

THANK YOU FOR BUYING MY ARTWORK, I PRAY FOR YOU THAT WE WILL ACHIEVE LITTLE OR BIG HAPPINESS
